No. 10-10994 (10A1219). Eddie Duval Powell, Petitioner v. Alabama. 564 U.S. 1015, 131 S. Ct. 3017,

180 L. Ed. 2d 841,

Application for stay of *842execution of sentence of death, presented to Justice Thomas, and by him referred to the Court, denied. Petition for writ of certiorari to the Supreme Court of Alabama denied.
